    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a reliable daily driver for someone willing to put in a little work. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable scratches, a few small dings, and fading clear coat on the roof, while the interior has some staining on the upholstery and minor wear on the driver's seat. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid, honest car that is priced to reflect its current state and maintenance needs.",
      "price": 21500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
